elationship or is that only the case when comparing English and Malagasy? %0a%3c %0a%3c Sources: https://phoible.org/inventories/view/31#tipa%0a%3c https://wals.info/feature/2A#2/19.3/152.8%0a%3c https://phoible.org/inventories/view/160#tipa%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
